---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Navan Hart" description="A rare memory animal of Vaelinya.">
  <section class="page-section">
    <p class="eyebrow">World · Animals</p>
    <h1>Navan Hart</h1>
    <p class="lede">A rare deerlike memory animal that appears where a place has remembered a truth clearly enough to begin healing.</p>

    <article class="visual-callout visual-callout-memory">
      <div class="visual-callout-mark" aria-hidden="true"><span>Na</span></div>
      <div class="visual-callout-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Mythic and rare</p>
        <h2>A sign of remembered truth</h2>
        <p>The Navan Hart is a rare memory animal and witness animal. It is not a pet, monster, or ordinary deer. It appears rarely, and its appearance matters.</p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
      <h2>How to recognise it</h2>
      <p>A Navan Hart has a deep brown body, moon-white antlers, calm dark eyes, small dark marks along the neck like old writing or old route marks, and a quiet step.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
      <h2>Sound and sign</h2>
      <p>The Navan Hart is almost silent. Its hooves make a soft double step even when it walks alone.</p>
      <p>The double step matters because it suggests that memory is never walking by itself.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
      <h2>Movement</h2>
      <p>It walks slowly. It may pause, look toward a path, then vanish behind trees, mist, a hill bend, an old road turn, or meadow light.</p>
      <p>It should not appear dramatically. It should feel as if the world has briefly allowed it to be seen.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
      <h2>Why it is rare</h2>
      <p>The Navan Hart appears only where memory has been carried truthfully rather than hidden, denied, or wasted.</p>
      <p>Its appearance means: this place has remembered enough to begin healing.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
      <h2>Related pages</h2>
      <div class="link-list">
        <a href="/artefacts/symbols/navan/">NAVAN symbol</a>
        <a href="/world/warm-remembering/">The Warm Remembering</a>
        <a href="/world/animals/">Animals of Vaelinya</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
      <p class="eyebrow">Accessibility note</p>
      <p>The Navan Hart is a rare deerlike animal with pale antlers. It appears where a place has remembered a truth clearly enough to begin healing.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
